<br>
1) park raid at zone in<br>
2) group with rogue + someone to be coth anchor<br>
3) run down to locked door outside of old safehall<br>
4) have the rogue hide/sneak/whatever they do<br>
5) coth rogue<br>
6) rogue opens door<br>
7) both step inside<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  coth everyone to the ledge, between doorway &amp; top step<br>
<br>
Then, have the rogue open the door &amp; have the raid rush out &amp; right, kill the 2-3 mobs there so you have room to work with.<br>
<br>
If you want prince, pull to that room, if you want king/queen, pull 'safehall' room to that corner room, ae it, move down to safe hall, pull library to 'safehall', ae it, move to library, pull old herb to library, ae it, pull king room, ae it while meeles split king &amp; kill him, move to king room, split queen room however you want (best is to pull queen to top of ramp &amp; hail with ally faction pc &amp; ae room), port out. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=412980">Lorcann</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=412968" target="top">Gallerus</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
