<br>
Not the prince's door with 2 guards outside, but the door leading to the corridor with 6-8 guards. You have 2 static mobs in the room to your left and 3 mobs to your right. further right is the Prince's Door w/ 2 guards. Outside that door I've CR'd upwards of 48 people and rezzed them all w/o agro.  <br>
<br>
You can also CoH behind Niblek fairly reliably, if you were looking to farmt he herb shack or something. Best to coh an invis enc/shm to CC, then tank, then healer, etc...  <p><CENTER>
